{"id": "art-45", "label": "Art. 45", "title": "Art. 45: Procedura de reunire a cauzelor", "slug": "art-45", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 45: Procedura de reunire a cauzelor </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1718768960\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2746\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1718768960\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Reunirea cauzelor se poate dispune la cererea\nprocurorului, a p&#259;r&#355;ilor, a persoanei v&#259;t&#259;mate &#351;i din\noficiu de c&#259;tre instan&#355;a competent&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Cauzele se pot reuni dac&#259;\nele se afl&#259; în fa&#355;a primei instan&#355;e, chiar dup&#259;\ndesfiin&#355;area sau casarea hot&#259;rârii, sau în fa&#355;a instan&#355;ei\nde apel.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Instan&#355;a se\npronun&#355;&#259; prin încheiere care poate fi atacat&#259; numai odat&#259;\ncu fondul.</span></p>"}